video.title: Cesar 911
video.synopsis: Canine expert extraordinaire Cesar Millan travels around the nation to help troubled dogs that are threatening the balance of their communities.

episodes.synopsis: Cesar comes to the rescue of a black Lab mix named Misty, who many feel should be put down because she has bitten every member of her household.
episodes.title: Family Feud

episodes.synopsis: Cesar meets with a Freedom Writers Foundation teacher who provides leadership to her at-risk students but can't seem to control her disruptive Lab.
episodes.title: Boss with a Bark

episodes.synopsis: Cesar works with two boxers that have been terrorizing their neighborhood and helps a dance teacher stop her Chihuahua from attacking students.
episodes.title: Dog Fight

episodes.synopsis: Cesar comes to the rescue of a dangerous Rottweiler whose vicious behavior is putting its owner's future as a professional football player at risk.
episodes.title: Attack Dogs

episodes.synopsis: Cesar is called to rehabilitate an aggressive pit bull, Titan, who is threatening his owner's relationship with his girlfriend.
episodes.title: Ripped Apart

episodes.synopsis: Cesar is challenged by a couple who desperately wants to save their pit bull-Lab mix from being put down after attacking a neighbor.
episodes.title: Neighborhood Bully
